  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Signed transactions I submit using the `eth_sendRawTransaction` RPC are not being incorporated into blocks.  The problem seems to be that raw transactions are not being added to the txpool.  Logging `self.backend.TxPool().GetTransactions()` immediately after `TxPool().Add` is called in [PushTx](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/98f4c936f25de27dbc90f36f2c1ffd1f23b114e9/xeth/xeth.go#L771) shows an empty txpool:\n\n```\n%!(EXTRA types.Transactions=[])\n```\n\nThe transaction itself looks ok, though:\n\n```\n%!(EXTRA *types.Transaction=\n    TX(465e4df1372b94f8b5486983dddb9a3d54ea033d4cabd967c15f64423e4106ec)\n    Contract: false\n    From:     8915c5ccc858f714c85ca4c31b15c7196cbb01f0\n    To:       abe47f122a496a732d6c4b38b3ca376d597d75dd\n    Nonce:    1338\n    GasPrice: 1147602752650\n    GasLimit  3135000\n    Value:    0\n    Data:     0x988445fe00000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000f69b5\n    V:        0x1b\n    R:        0x829374c161d106f9cc5aa901f3be878843e48d9f77a7325d22c94c03671f5408\n    S:        0x691b4cb4dadf036ba152f3627849661ecf7edf97bc294e25637781133f2e96f4\n    Hex:      f88c82053a86010b3274548a832fd61894abe47f122a496a732d6c4b38b3ca376d597d75dd80a4988445fe00000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000f69b51ba0829374c161d106f9cc5aa901f3be878843e48d9f77a7325d22c94c03671f5408a0691b4cb4dadf036ba152f3627849661ecf7edf97bc294e25637781133f2e96f4\n)\n```\n\nI'm using Geth/v0.9.39-12bb743b/linux/go1.4.2.\n",
